10:
Why... Why am I still not good
enough?!
18:
I hate that stupid face of yours! Stop
looking at me like that!
23: I've had enough of your pity!
43: I'm sick and tired of YOU!
62: "This is impossible. I can't do this."
65:
Isn't that right? You're all alone, and
no one's here to save you.
69:
...That's fine. I think we all know what
it's like to struggle alone.
89:
A world for only you and me. A place
free of judgement.
105:
Gotta say, the expression you've got
now is much cuter.
116:
I've gotten more powerful... I should
be as strong as Tohru!
120: There's no way I'll lose here!
125: Heh... This the best you can do?
127: No wonder your knees are shaking.
135:
You wanna know what real strength
is? It's not pretending you've got no
weaknesses...
138:
It's getting up and fighting no
matter how many times life knocks
you down!
151:
Kids these days... No place for
crybabies on the battlefield.
154:
Heh... They're having a party up
there, huh?
160:
Come, Stella. We should give them a
moment.
173:
You won. Boss lady's all yours. I'm
sick of looking at your face anyway.
184:
You knew I liked Yuki from the
beginning.
187:
But you pretended not to know, and
I played along!
195:
Did you really think I was stupid
enough not to notice? Or was it
some kinda game to you?
198:
Did you get a kick outta being nice
to me?
202:
"Oh, poor Sho. I'll at least give him
some attention because I'm the
better person!"
206:
Bet you thought I was desperate
enough to want your fake friendship!
215:
You just ASSUMED I thought those
things?
219:
...Being with you just makes me
miserable.
222:
Go away... I don't need your pity
anymore.
231:
That's why I was afraid that you'd be
the one to leave me behind one day.
234:
But I guess if that's how you really
saw us... Maybe there wasn't
anything to leave behind in the first
place.
253:
Soon, we shall be freed from this
nightmare!
260: Oh... Is this the power of... our god?
261: I can feel it flowing through me!
270:
So it's true. You've been using the Iris
to give people powers.
275:
Tell mewho do you seek to bring
salvation to?
279:
You desire the power to cross the
Void and determine your own
destiny... But not for yourself. For
someone else, yes?
286:
Only I am capable of opening the
Iris.
289: Then I'll just have to take you with it.
